99-0649 (La. 4/23/99)

Lisa Winters McCLELLAND on Behalf of the Minor Child, Alexandra Ann WINTERS v. Abby James BROUSSARD. No. 99-C-0649. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Broussard, Abby James; — Defendants); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review; Parish of Lafayette 15th Judicial District Court Div. “C” Number 88-4228; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CA98-0906

Denied.

VICTORY, J. would grant the writ. TRAYLOR, J. not on panel.
